{
  "stem": "22972.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I attended the closing ceremonies of the Olympics, not far from Hitler, where all the German school children-- those wonderful Aryan school children-- were allowed to sit.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of course, you-- everybody knows about Jesse Owens, so I don't have to mention anything about that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You also know about the Jewish-- German Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what-- what-- what came out of the Olympics was that, as soon as the last journalist had left the city, the antisemitism was put back into place in triple force. 13 new edicts came out the week after the last journalist had left Berlin.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was no longer permitted for a Jew to be married to a Gentile-- to a pure Aryan.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hitler started sterilization.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's one of the quirks of history, of fate, of nature, whatever you want to call it, that Hitler had the misfortune-- and that the world had the fortune-- that Hitler was born with black hair.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had the blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If-- there are papers have been found that, if Hitler had not had black hair, he had planned to sterilize even good Aryans after he had eliminated all of the Jews, obviously, after that final solution.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had planned to sterilize all Germans who were not blond or blue eyed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He couldn't get himself to do it, because he himself had black hair.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In '36, the teachers were told that they could no longer talk to us in class.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In I don't know whether it was the end of '36 or after Christmas vacation of 1937 that the classrooms all over Germany were rearranged.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the-- until then, in school in Germany, you sat alphabetically.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
